\h #dPASSWORD \d

\uUSAGE\n
#dpassword name password

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Change a player's password.
Note that you must provide the full PC name of the player whose password you wish to change.

For information regarding the ethical use of this command, see "help ethics".

\uEXAMPLES\n
\q#dpassword taro Aoeu1\d to change Taro's password to "Aoeu1".4`
